name: Goodbye, My Coney Island Baby

(return again)

So goodbye...

(de hi)

Goodbye my Coney Isle...

Army of married fools

To the alter

(just like leading lambs to slaughter)

Oh boy we get it good.

Bachelor days we then recall!

(we then recall)

Doctor Lawyer, Merchant, Chief.

We all are bound for:
